Data Model Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Define and link data objects with portals, integrate variable associations, and optimize your application's data-driven functionality.
Interface Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Interface is the form builder which includes the form canvas, controls, data objects, and variety of other options for creating and customizing form.

Controls Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Controls are the form elements used to take input from the user in variety of formats such as text, number, date, & so on.

Templates Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Consists of system & user defined form templates for application creation.

Caching Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Enables caching for data optimization.

ReadOnly Style Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Allows data to be rendered in a read-only format, making it unmodifiable.

Cache Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA It allows to save the data temporarily in special storage.
SaveEncrypted Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA It allows to save the data in encrypted form. It ensures data security.
AutoComplete Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA It predicts what you want to type next based on the text you've already entered. It reduces errors and speeds up your work.
Masking Pattern Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA It allows input of data in predefined data patterns for example, password, and so on.

ZoneList Advanced Tooltip Content: Arabic-SA Enables mapping of the zone created for data extraction.
